title: Eyes That See In the Dark (1983) by Kenny Rogers
description:
This album was made in 1983. by Barry, Robin & Maurice Gibb and Alby Galuthen for Kenny Rogers.

Contains 10 songs, of which No.2 is in duet with Dolly Parton

 1. Eyes That See In the Dark
 2. Islands In the Stream
 3. You And I
 4. Midsummer Nights
 5. This Woman
 6. Buried Treasure
 7. Hold Me
 8. Evening Star
 9. I Will Always Love You
10. Living With You


Front cover : Kenny Rogers, background contains blue & white abstract design ;

Back cover: beautiful sunset at Grand Canyon, CO, USA ;

Inside photo : Kenny Rogers en-face ;

Inside list : all ten songs with their original lyrics

note : "Midsummer Nights"`s second strophe is not presented in the song
